step.html_instructions: Take the 1st right to stay on Victoria Square
Turn left onto Main North Rd/Princes Hwy/A1 (signs for National Highway A1/Gepps Cross)

Keep left at the fork
Continue to follow Princes Hwy/A1

Slight left onto Port Wakefield Rd/Princes Hwy/A1
Continue to follow Port Wakefield Rd/Princes Hwy
Take the ramp onto Northern Expressway/National Highway M20
Take the National Route A32 ramp to Tarlee

Turn left onto Main North Rd/National Route A32
Continue to follow Main North Rd
Go through 1 roundabout
Destination will be on the right

Head southeast on Main North Rd/B82 toward Ness St
Continue to follow Main North Rd
Go through 1 roundabout
Merge onto Sturt Hwy/National Highway A20 via the ramp to Nuriootpa
Head south on Barossa Valley Way/B19 toward Oak St

Turn left onto Lyndoch Valley Rd/B31
Continue to follow B31
B31 turns slightly left and becomes Mount Crawford Rd

Turn left onto Cricks Mill Rd/B35
Continue to follow B35
Turn right onto Birdwood Rd/B10 (signs for TORRENS VALLEY SCENIC DRIVE)

Continue straight to stay on Princes Hwy/B55
Continue to follow Princes Hwy
Turn left onto Princes Hwy/National Highway A1 (signs for Tailem Bend)

Turn right onto Riddoch Hwy/A66 (signs for Naracoorte/Mount Gambier)
Go through 1 roundabout

Turn right to stay on Riddoch Hwy/A66
Destination will be on the right
Head south on Riddoch Hwy/A66 toward Tricia Reschke Rd

Turn left to stay on Riddoch Hwy/A66
Go through 1 roundabout
Turn left onto Dukes Hwy/National Highway A8 (signs for Coonalpyn/Adelaide)

Continue onto Princes Hwy/National Highway A1
Continue to follow National Highway A1
Continue onto South Eastern Freeway/National Highway M1

Slight right to stay on Adelaide Rd/Tourist Drive 57
Go through 1 roundabout
At the roundabout, take the 3rd exit onto Flaxley Rd/Tourist Drive 57

Take the 2nd left onto Angus Rd/Strathalbyn Rd/Tourist Drive 57
Continue to follow Tourist Drive 57

Take the 2nd left onto Brookman Rd/B34
Continue to follow B34

Continue onto Main Rd
Destination will be on the left

Turn right onto Victor Harbor Rd/A13
Continue to follow A13
Slight left onto Main South Rd/A13 (signs for South Road/City)
